snippet.title: Night Mind
snippet.description:
The internet's source for all the dark, mysterious, horrifying, and strange things to be found in this world's realm, hosted by one of them himself. Used to be my mother's most disappointing son, but now I'm here to be your least disappointing interdimensional shapeshifting monster cat host! Reviews, explanations, stories, and more. 

Once the sun falls, it's time to open up your Night Mind.
